# ─── REQUIRED: Backend URL (for the watch page to function) ───
# On Vercel: you can leave this EMPTY — the app auto-detects VERCEL_URL.
# On local dev: defaults to http://localhost:3000/api (same-origin proxy).
# Override only if you want to point to a different backend.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL=""

# ─── OPTIONAL: Consumet API instance (for real anime streaming) ───
# Self-host Consumet: https://github.com/consumet/api.consumet.org
# ⚠️ The public api.consumet.org endpoint is DEAD (HTTP 451). Must self-host.
# CONSUMET_URL="https://your-consumet-instance.com"
